 <br>
Ya know,cast or sing,learn what it is,what it does,an' so forth.<br>
 <br>
I pack a Kael mask fer just such occasions. So I DO know when it's unclean filth.<br>
 <br>
I can even prove some fella follows my god when I need ta,real simple. Say ya wanted ta join a guild I was in,an' ya had ta worship Innoruuk ta get in.<br>
 <br>
Here's an imbued Idol of Innoruuk. Ya say ya worship Him?<br>
 <br>
Equip this an' prove it. Or fer that matter,lemme get an imbued silver sapphire necklace made. Might be cheaper. Same result. Some folk got it even cheaper. Silver jade or amber is right cheap. :P<br>
An' in case yer wondering,t'application fee is five hundred platinum,paid _in advance_ in case ya decided ta scoot with m'idol...deposit returned when t'idol is. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
 <br>
So there ya go. I can make sure yer a follower of ANY dark god,just wit' a little somethin' blessed by t'right priest or shaman.<br>
 <br>
Wish I could craft somethin' simpler ta prove it. Hmm,that's somethin' ta ponder...but ya get t'idea. What people are,an' what things are is somethin' easily discerned fer any but t'youngest adventurers-an' considerin'  merchants usually have some sorta magickal guild near ta em,I don't doubt they have easy ways ta know what's what too.<br>
 <br>
-Morgrist<br>
